              "number": 4949,
              "url": "https://github.com/webpack/webpack/issues/4949",
              "body": "Given existing module webpack should be able to understand analyze and import dependencies of WASM modules. Must follow the same resolving rules for modules.\r\n\r\nsomemodule.wasm (given in .wast format)\r\n```wast\r\n(module\r\n (import “./math” “random” (func rand (result f32))\r\n (func\r\n  (export \"addRandom\")\r\n  (param i32)\r\n  (result i32)\r\n  (i32.add (get_local 0) (call rand))\r\n )\r\n)\r\n```",
